      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BELTONE BOY (2) has a strong record this track and trip with six wins and six placings from 18 starts. Below best last time at this track (23.37) in a NG, finishing a 8 length sixth. Looks suited here and rates on top. ELLA KNOWS (5) could manage only second at this track last time but caught the eye when posting a handy 22.88 over 400m at this track three starts ago. Top win three back and rates a key player again. STOP IT ZIPPER (1) turned spotting a big start finishing seventh (22.98) last time in a Grade 4 at Gosford. Has a good record here including 10 wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. Has ability and can measure up. DAPHNE ZACAPA (3) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
